FuncDef: The display authentication user-alarm configuration command displays alarm thresholds for the percentage of successfully authenticated NAC users. The display authentication user-alarm configuration command displays alarm thresholds for the percentage of successfully authenticated NAC users. This command is supported only on the CE6863H, CE6863H-K, CE6881H, CE6881H-K, CE6820H, CE6820H-K and CE6820S.
